# üè† Homepage

## Story 1: View Welcome Message

### Title:
As a user, I want to see a personalized welcome message with my name on the homepage, so that I feel recognized and can confirm I am logged into the correct account.

### Acceptance Criteria:

1. Homepage displays ‚ÄúWelcome, [User Name]‚Äù.

2. User name fetched from profile or registration details.

3. Updated name reflects instantly after profile change.

* Priority: Medium
* Story Points: 2

Notes:
* Personalization helps user confirm active account.

## Story 2: Display Weekly Progress

### Title:
As a user, I want to see my daily progress for each habit on the homepage, so that I can easily monitor my progress.

### Acceptance Criteria:

1. Homepage displays progress tracker for all active habits.

2. Each habit shows daily completion indicators.

3. Progress updates automatically when habits are marked complete.

* Priority: High
* Story Points: 3

### Notes:
* Progress displayed using a bar, graph, or streak counter.

# Story 3: View Completed Habits

### Title:
As a user, I want to see a section for completed habits on the homepage, so that I can track what I have already achieved.

### Acceptance Criteria:

1. Completed habits appear in a separate section.

2. Each shows completion date or streak.

3. Completed section updates dynamically.

* Priority: Medium
* Story Points: 2

!! Notes:
* Section hidden if no habits are completed.
